skins.shipDescription: It's nice to meet you! From what I've heard, you're the "Commander," right? I'm Misaki. I have experience with various part-time jobs, so... I'm confident that I can be of help to you all. Let's do our best!
skins.selfIntroduction: You want me to introduce myself? I'm Misaki, and my hobbies include scuba diving, stargazing, and... reading comics, I guess. Also, I really like mango vanilla crêpes and bubble milk tea! Oh, right, and... be nice to my sister, Nagisa!
skins.acquisition: It's nice to meet you! From what I've heard, you're the "Commander," right? I'm Misaki. I have experience with various part-time jobs, so... I'm confident that I can be of help to you all. Let's do our best!
skins.login: Commander, hurry up~ Let's get to work, shall we?
skins.details: I get these weird vibes from this port and the shipgirls that live here... But most of all, I get them from you, Commander. Oh, I'm just messing with you! Ahaha!
skins.secretaryIdle1: If you've got nothing else for me to do, I'm gonna head off to my part-time job... wait, I guess this is one, too...?
skins.secretaryIdle2: Mm~ I could go for some sweets right about now. Maybe a crêpe or something...
skins.secretaryIdle3: My sister might be scary at times, but she's a nice person at heart! ...Though, she might be a bit on the overprotective side...
skins.secretaryTouch: Yeees? Did you call for me, Commander?
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Wah?! Geez, I'll be really angry if you do that again!
skins.secretaryHeadpat: Hey, um... This feels odd to me...

skins.JPClientName: 特eなゴ`ルデンセッション
skins.shipDescription: A photoshoot? That'd be similar to what I did before coming here, but... um, this swimsuit is a bit much... Commander, is this what you're into? Geez... It's so embarrassing...
skins.acquisition: A photoshoot? That'd be similar to what I did before coming here, but... um, this swimsuit is a bit much... Commander, is this what you're into? Geez... It's so embarrassing...
skins.login: We're doing another shoot today? I don't mind, but...
skins.details: Commander, did you ask my sister to participate in some photoshoots too? Hehe~ She might act all mean on the outside, but she'll do whatever you need as long as you don't ask for something risqué~
skins.secretaryIdle1: After the shoot, wanna go grab some bubble milk tea? All right, no backsies!
skins.secretaryIdle2: Commander, are you taking some photos of the other girls as well? Let me have a look~
skins.secretaryIdle3: Commander, if you could go on a trip, where would you go?
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: N-no, you can't! It's too embarrassing...
